<L>__{exterior behind the world of donuts day}
<A>__{moments later. he comes walking up a small alley and sits to drink his beer. he begins to relax. this is his quality private time. then he hears something and looks up. he peeks up over the edge of some junked kitchen appliances and sees... two teenage kids warren and amy smoking crack and having sex. simon looks on, intrigued, as warren smokes, then...}
<C>__{warren}
<P>__{(to amy)}
<D>__{you want some?}
<A>__{amy takes the pipe and smokes as he feels her up. simon is fascinated. he drinks and looks on as... amy grins up foolishly at warren and lowers the pipe. the boy undoes his belt and hikes up the girl's skirt. simon can't believe this. he looks around to see if the coast is clear, then returns just in time to see... warren takes amy by the waist and enter her. the pipe falls from the young girl's hand. warren throws his head back and grinds himself into her. simon's mouth falls open in awe. but amy tosses her head back to the side and sees... the amazed garbage man; caught. amy starts screaming insanely. simon runs for his life. amy and warren throw rocks and bottles at him as they chase him away.}
